1
00:00:07,591 --> 00:00:11,220
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Rick] <i>Ugh. Guess this is how it ends.
I thought I was better than this.</i></font>

2
00:00:11,303 --> 00:00:14,181
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Dramatic voiceover while stranded in space?</i></font>

3
00:00:14,264 --> 00:00:17,392
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>I guess when you're dying,
the first thing to go is your creativity.</i></font>

4
00:00:18,268 --> 00:00:22,564
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Citadel's gone
and the saucer we escaped in is out of power.</i></font>

5
00:00:22,648 --> 00:00:24,149
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm so scared in here.</font>

6
00:00:24,233 --> 00:00:25,901
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Rick] <i>The extra Mortys went feral.</i></font>

7
00:00:25,984 --> 00:00:27,152
<font face="Serif" size="18">[screams]</font>

8
00:00:27,236 --> 00:00:29,112
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Ah. Some problems solve themselves.</i></font>

9
00:00:29,821 --> 00:00:32,950
<font face="Serif" size="18">Been drinking a lot-- Morty, write this down.</font>

10
00:00:33,033 --> 00:00:35,953
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't have a helmet like that Avengers guy did.</font>

11
00:00:36,036 --> 00:00:38,080
<font face="Serif" size="18">Been drinking a lot of my piss.</font>

12
00:00:38,163 --> 00:00:39,873
<font face="Serif" size="18">Portal gun's still broken--</font>

13
00:00:39,957 --> 00:00:44,586
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I guess that was all part of Evil Morty's plan.
- Evil Morty? Can we stop flattering this guy?</font>

14
00:00:44,670 --> 00:00:46,463
<font face="Serif" size="18">His plan was to monologue and fuck off.</font>

15
00:00:46,547 --> 00:00:49,591
<font face="Serif" size="18">He basically threw a tantrum
to announce he was quitting Twitter.</font>

16
00:00:49,675 --> 00:00:51,093
<font face="Serif" size="18">Nobody quits Twitter.</font>

17
00:00:51,969 --> 00:00:53,971
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey, remember, like, a second ago</font>

18
00:00:54,054 --> 00:00:57,683
<font face="Serif" size="18">when you pretended not to know
who Iron Man was? Who was that for?</font>

19
00:00:57,766 --> 00:01:01,603
<font face="Serif" size="18">Shush, shush, Morty.
This is how we go. Bear it with grace.</font>

20
00:01:01,687 --> 00:01:05,566
<font face="Serif" size="18">Spinal cord, Robitussin as a base,
then surprise me.</font>

21
00:01:05,649 --> 00:01:07,109
<font face="Serif" size="18">[groaning]</font>

22
00:01:12,656 --> 00:01:13,949
<font face="Serif" size="18">[tapping on glass]</font>

23
00:01:16,118 --> 00:01:17,327
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Mom!
- Beth, maybe!</font>

24
00:01:17,411 --> 00:01:18,412
<font face="Serif" size="18">[inaudible dialogue]</font>

25
00:01:18,495 --> 00:01:21,665
<font face="Serif" size="18">Is she trying to say something?
We can't hear you.</font>

26
00:01:22,249 --> 00:01:26,962
<font face="Serif" size="18">How dumb are--? Beth, you're in a vacuum.
Sound travels on air. Why am I yelling?</font>

27
00:01:30,674 --> 00:01:32,259
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Wow, great.
- Yeah, that's-- Wow.</font>

28
00:01:32,342 --> 00:01:34,303
<font face="Serif" size="18">Really worth it. That was not worth it.</font>

29
00:01:34,386 --> 00:01:36,680
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's corny. You. Corn.</font>

30
00:01:36,763 --> 00:01:38,932
<font face="Serif" size="18">Dying of starvation here.</font>

31
00:01:39,516 --> 00:01:42,394
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, my God. Stop explaining. Stop explaining!</font>

32
00:01:42,477 --> 00:01:44,062
<font face="Serif" size="18">Are you finished?</font>

33
00:01:44,146 --> 00:01:45,314
<font face="Serif" size="18">She's not finished.</font>

34
00:01:46,315 --> 00:01:48,358
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Nice.
- Real mature. Real classy.</font>

35
00:01:48,442 --> 00:01:49,860
<font face="Serif" size="18">[theme music playing]</font>

36
00:02:23,268 --> 00:02:25,145
<font face="Serif" size="18">- It was a good line.
- I didn't need it to be.</font>

37
00:02:25,228 --> 00:02:28,315
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I don't care what you think.
- Oh, my God. She found you. Eat.</font>

38
00:02:28,398 --> 00:02:29,274
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, hell, yes.</font>

39
00:02:29,358 --> 00:02:32,027
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hold on, buddy.
Our systems could go into shock from solid food.</font>

40
00:02:32,110 --> 00:02:34,821
<font face="Serif" size="18">Digestibot, convert to nutrient mass.</font>

41
00:02:43,705 --> 00:02:44,915
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm just gonna risk it.</font>

42
00:02:45,415 --> 00:02:47,668
<font face="Serif" size="18">Since when do you guys get stranded?</font>

43
00:02:47,751 --> 00:02:49,920
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Thank you.
- Almost left them there.</font>

44
00:02:50,003 --> 00:02:51,546
<font face="Serif" size="18">Portal travel's broken. Mm.</font>

45
00:02:51,630 --> 00:02:54,633
<font face="Serif" size="18">Are these heirloom tomatoes?
Digestibot, try these.</font>

46
00:02:54,716 --> 00:02:56,927
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Yum, yum.
- You can't hop realities anymore?</font>

47
00:02:57,010 --> 00:02:59,054
<font face="Serif" size="18">That mean you'll finally have to wash your robe?</font>

48
00:02:59,137 --> 00:03:01,682
<font face="Serif" size="18">Good point.
I need to reboot the portal index immediately.</font>

49
00:03:02,683 --> 00:03:04,976
<font face="Serif" size="18">Basically a hard reset on the fluid.</font>

50
00:03:05,060 --> 00:03:07,020
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hold tight. The Earth's gonna shake a bit.</font>

51
00:03:17,864 --> 00:03:19,991
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Um...
- Oh.</font>

52
00:03:20,075 --> 00:03:22,244
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Oh, shit.
- Wait. What? What's happening?</font>

53
00:03:22,327 --> 00:03:26,206
<font face="Serif" size="18">Instead of resetting portal travel,
I may have reset portal travelers.</font>

54
00:03:26,289 --> 00:03:27,708
<font face="Serif" size="18">Too late to apologize.</font>

55
00:03:27,791 --> 00:03:29,960
<font face="Serif" size="18">Rick, why am I pulsing green?</font>

56
00:03:30,043 --> 00:03:32,337
<font face="Serif" size="18">Don't say you don't know,
because you're pulsing green.</font>

57
00:03:32,421 --> 00:03:35,298
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Are we about to die?
- No, we're about to vanish from this reality.</font>

58
00:03:35,382 --> 00:03:36,925
<font face="Serif" size="18">- That's totally dying.
- No, it isn't.</font>

59
00:03:37,008 --> 00:03:40,137
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's everyone from this reality
returning to their reality of origin.</font>

60
00:03:40,220 --> 00:03:43,056
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Back to our original universes.
- I explained it fine, Morty.</font>

61
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:45,183
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're spoon-feeding spoons.
Where's Summer?</font>

62
00:03:45,267 --> 00:03:46,977
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, nice. You guys are back. Whoa.</font>

63
00:03:47,060 --> 00:03:50,063
<font face="Serif" size="18">Three of us are one-way blind-hopping.
You gotta help us get back.</font>

64
00:03:50,147 --> 00:03:53,066
<font face="Serif" size="18">There's protocol for this
in your chores server, file name booger-aids.</font>

65
00:03:53,150 --> 00:03:55,610
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Every file is booger-aids.
- I hate naming things.</font>

66
00:03:55,694 --> 00:03:59,072
<font face="Serif" size="18">Just search for words
like "one-way blind-hop, reset nav beacon."</font>

67
00:03:59,156 --> 00:04:01,908
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Why do I have a reality of origin?
- No time to explain, Jerry.</font>

68
00:04:01,992 --> 00:04:04,911
<font face="Serif" size="18">Counting on you, Summer.
One-way blind-hop beacon protocol.</font>

69
00:04:04,995 --> 00:04:08,290
<font face="Serif" size="18">Here we go!</font>

70
00:04:11,293 --> 00:04:12,669
<font face="Serif" size="18">So there was time to explain.</font>

71
00:04:12,753 --> 00:04:15,338
<font face="Serif" size="18">Don't waste extra precious seconds
with your pettiness, Jerry.</font>

72
00:04:15,422 --> 00:04:18,383
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Summer, let's run down--
- One-way blind-hop reset beacon. Booger-aids.</font>

73
00:04:18,467 --> 00:04:19,301
<font face="Serif" size="18">Cool.</font>

74
00:04:21,261 --> 00:04:23,305
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Wow.
- There was so much time to explain!</font>

75
00:04:23,388 --> 00:04:26,600
<font face="Serif" size="18">Fine. Hindsight is 20-20.
Who has ever taken this long to vanish?</font>

76
00:04:26,683 --> 00:04:29,060
<font face="Serif" size="18">How did I end up not in my own universe?</font>

77
00:04:29,144 --> 00:04:30,812
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, my God. The Jerryboree.</font>

78
00:04:30,896 --> 00:04:32,939
<font face="Serif" size="18">[both] The Jerryboree!</font>

79
00:04:33,023 --> 00:04:33,899
<font face="Serif" size="18">Deep cut.</font>

80
00:04:35,984 --> 00:04:38,612
<font face="Serif" size="18">But where's our real Dad and our real Morty?</font>

81
00:04:38,695 --> 00:04:40,155
<font face="Serif" size="18">Buried in the backyard.</font>

82
00:04:40,238 --> 00:04:42,032
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's what the possums are after.</font>

83
00:04:46,036 --> 00:04:48,455
<font face="Serif" size="18">Dad's got you in the family business too?</font>

84
00:04:48,538 --> 00:04:51,458
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, Morty is an easy mark,
but Rick pays me in things like...</font>

85
00:04:52,626 --> 00:04:54,211
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wolverine claws.</font>

86
00:04:54,294 --> 00:04:57,547
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, looks like you got this.
See you guys in another two years?</font>

87
00:04:57,631 --> 00:04:59,841
<font face="Serif" size="18">Or you could stick around for this one.</font>

88
00:04:59,925 --> 00:05:03,970
<font face="Serif" size="18">Looks like it involves Grandpa's grotty citadel.
We could, you know, break things, loot stuff.</font>

89
00:05:04,054 --> 00:05:07,849
<font face="Serif" size="18">I should probably get back to saving the galaxy.</font>

90
00:05:07,933 --> 00:05:09,434
<font face="Serif" size="18">Please?</font>

91
00:05:09,518 --> 00:05:12,729
<font face="Serif" size="18">Uh, guess I could loot some stuff.
Fine. Let's make it quick.</font>

92
00:05:12,813 --> 00:05:16,233
<font face="Serif" size="18">Awesome. I've never been.
Let's do this. Adventure family.</font>

93
00:05:16,316 --> 00:05:17,651
<font face="Serif" size="18">Whoo!</font>

94
00:05:17,734 --> 00:05:19,569
<font face="Serif" size="18">Uh, okay.</font>

95
00:05:24,115 --> 00:05:25,200
<font face="Serif" size="18">Fuck.</font>

96
00:05:30,872 --> 00:05:34,125
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Excuse me? Bro, Ricks don't pass on this.</i></font>

97
00:05:36,670 --> 00:05:38,630
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Diane] <i>Rick, is that you?</i></font>

98
00:05:38,713 --> 00:05:40,507
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, Diane.</font>

99
00:05:40,590 --> 00:05:43,718
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>You've been gone so long.
Did you find our daughter's killer?</i></font>

100
00:05:43,802 --> 00:05:45,887
<font face="Serif" size="18">Not yet, sorry. Still looking.</font>

101
00:05:45,971 --> 00:05:50,058
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>You'll find him.
You always do everything you set your mind to,</i></font>

102
00:05:50,141 --> 00:05:53,436
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>except keep your family alive.
But that was hardly your fault.</i></font>

103
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:54,354
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mute.</font>

104
00:05:54,855 --> 00:06:00,026
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>If I could be muted, I wouldn't be too good
at haunting you, would I, you dirty bear?</i></font>

105
00:06:00,110 --> 00:06:03,697
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I forgot I wanted to be haunted.
- <i>You predicted you might.</i></font>

106
00:06:03,780 --> 00:06:05,782
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>That's where haunting comes in handy, huh?</i></font>

107
00:06:05,866 --> 00:06:07,492
<font face="Serif" size="18">Very good point, sugar.</font>

108
00:06:14,666 --> 00:06:15,959
<font face="Serif" size="18">Rick?</font>

109
00:06:19,421 --> 00:06:21,381
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hello? Original family?</font>

110
00:06:21,464 --> 00:06:22,883
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sorry about last time.</font>

111
00:06:22,966 --> 00:06:25,135
<font face="Serif" size="18">Rick, he was in space prison.</font>

112
00:06:25,218 --> 00:06:27,262
<font face="Serif" size="18">We couldn't just-- Hello?</font>

113
00:06:27,345 --> 00:06:29,055
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [roaring]
- [screaming]</font>

114
00:06:32,893 --> 00:06:33,894
<font face="Serif" size="18">[screams]</font>

115
00:06:35,812 --> 00:06:36,897
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, jeez.</font>

116
00:06:40,150 --> 00:06:41,151
<font face="Serif" size="18">[gasps]</font>

117
00:06:55,165 --> 00:06:56,124
<font face="Serif" size="18">[sighs]</font>

118
00:06:59,586 --> 00:07:03,089
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ah. Fuck. Damn it, Morty.
There's no doctors anymore.</font>

119
00:07:03,173 --> 00:07:04,341
<font face="Serif" size="18">Dad?</font>

120
00:07:07,761 --> 00:07:09,846
<font face="Serif" size="18">Figures it's underwhelming the one time I visit.</font>

121
00:07:09,930 --> 00:07:13,391
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah. Sorry. Usually there's cowboy
Rick and Mortys and stuff.</font>

122
00:07:14,142 --> 00:07:17,103
<font face="Serif" size="18">Looks like they could use
a couple repairmen Rick and Mortys, right?</font>

123
00:07:18,021 --> 00:07:21,733
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, tight. Little scavenger dudes.
If they shoot at us, I'm allowed to...</font>

124
00:07:22,651 --> 00:07:25,195
<font face="Serif" size="18">do this. Shit, yeah.</font>

125
00:07:28,031 --> 00:07:29,616
<font face="Serif" size="18">Space Mom, get in on this.</font>

126
00:07:33,662 --> 00:07:36,623
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Cool Mom.
- Keep it moving. I don't have all day.</font>

127
00:07:37,666 --> 00:07:38,541
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Beth] I got it.</font>

128
00:07:39,459 --> 00:07:40,585
<font face="Serif" size="18">[screeching]</font>

129
00:07:40,669 --> 00:07:43,213
<font face="Serif" size="18">I got it. I got it. Sorry.</font>

130
00:07:44,130 --> 00:07:46,841
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sorry. I got it. Sorry.</font>

131
00:07:49,094 --> 00:07:50,929
<font face="Serif" size="18">I was gonna do it.</font>

132
00:07:51,012 --> 00:07:52,973
<font face="Serif" size="18">Terrestrials, am I right?</font>

133
00:07:53,473 --> 00:07:57,727
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Diane] <i>I kept up the search in your absence.
You want a new list of potential locations?</i></font>

134
00:07:57,811 --> 00:08:00,146
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're always just one room away, huh?</font>

135
00:08:00,230 --> 00:08:03,692
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Yeah. Remember, you thought
if you could see or touch me,</i></font>

136
00:08:03,775 --> 00:08:06,027
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>it might give you a level of com-com-comfort.</i></font>

137
00:08:06,111 --> 00:08:09,030
<font face="Serif" size="18">Right. Can't have that. Come on, Summer.</font>

138
00:08:09,114 --> 00:08:11,408
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Who's Summer? Should I be jealous?</i></font>

139
00:08:11,491 --> 00:08:14,786
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>I hope Summer knows
what happens to the people you love.</i></font>

140
00:08:14,869 --> 00:08:15,954
<font face="Serif" size="18">[doorbell rings]</font>

141
00:08:17,497 --> 00:08:18,581
<font face="Serif" size="18">[gun cocks]</font>

142
00:08:19,374 --> 00:08:20,333
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey, Rick.</font>

143
00:08:20,417 --> 00:08:22,502
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey, Mr. Goldmanbachmajorian.</font>

144
00:08:22,585 --> 00:08:24,462
<font face="Serif" size="18">Still alive, huh? What's up?</font>

145
00:08:24,546 --> 00:08:28,925
<font face="Serif" size="18">I was wondering if you could help me
make sense of a note I found this morning.</font>

146
00:08:29,009 --> 00:08:32,345
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's written by someone claiming to be me.</font>

147
00:08:32,429 --> 00:08:37,183
<font face="Serif" size="18">They say my mind is "held captive in a time loop,
trapped in the day of a traumatic event</font>

148
00:08:37,267 --> 00:08:42,105
<font face="Serif" size="18">by the agony of a formidable intelligence,
but also that my captor forgot about aging,</font>

149
00:08:42,188 --> 00:08:44,899
<font face="Serif" size="18">that my body spoils and yearns for death</font>

150
00:08:44,983 --> 00:08:49,029
<font face="Serif" size="18">while my soul remains stuck in place,
caught like a fly in amber."</font>

151
00:08:49,112 --> 00:08:51,364
<font face="Serif" size="18">Right. I used to "drink" drink.</font>

152
00:08:51,448 --> 00:08:53,658
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Uh, no clue, pal.
- That's okay.</font>

153
00:08:53,742 --> 00:08:55,785
<font face="Serif" size="18">I found other notes in the trash just like it.</font>

154
00:08:55,869 --> 00:08:59,414
<font face="Serif" size="18">Poor weirdo. I pity them.
Wish they could let go and move on.</font>

155
00:08:59,497 --> 00:09:01,416
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Sounds healthy.
- Sure would be.</font>

156
00:09:03,793 --> 00:09:05,712
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [Goldmanbachmajorian groaning]
- [thuds]</font>

157
00:09:05,795 --> 00:09:07,464
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Goldmanbachmajorian] Sweet death.</font>

158
00:09:07,547 --> 00:09:10,467
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Diane] <i>Was that symbolic? Are you letting go?</i></font>

159
00:09:10,550 --> 00:09:12,761
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>I understand, baby. I forgive you.</i></font>

160
00:09:12,844 --> 00:09:17,140
<font face="Serif" size="18">You don't get to say that. You're not her.
You're a thing I built to torture myself.</font>

161
00:09:17,223 --> 00:09:20,268
<font face="Serif" size="18">This timeline is cursed. I gotta get out of here.</font>

162
00:09:20,351 --> 00:09:21,895
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Because you wanna move on.</i></font>

163
00:09:21,978 --> 00:09:25,023
<font face="Serif" size="18">Because I don't.
[burps] And I have to.</font>

164
00:09:25,106 --> 00:09:26,733
<font face="Serif" size="18">I came back on accident.</font>

165
00:09:26,816 --> 00:09:30,028
<font face="Serif" size="18">Guy I'm looking for, he's not findable, Diane.</font>

166
00:09:31,571 --> 00:09:33,573
<font face="Serif" size="18">I live with a version of Beth now.</font>

167
00:09:33,656 --> 00:09:35,742
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Sounds like a version of nice.</i></font>

168
00:09:35,825 --> 00:09:39,788
<font face="Serif" size="18">We have grandkids. That's who Summer is.
She'll get me out of here.</font>

169
00:09:39,871 --> 00:09:41,206
<font face="Serif" size="18">She reminds me of you.</font>

170
00:09:41,289 --> 00:09:43,458
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Oh, really? Is she dead too?</i></font>

171
00:09:44,125 --> 00:09:45,085
<font face="Serif" size="18">Bye, Diane.</font>

172
00:09:45,168 --> 00:09:48,588
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>You're not honestly gonna fly into that rift
without coordinates, are you?</i></font>

173
00:09:48,671 --> 00:09:50,298
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Don't give up on us, Rick.</i></font>

174
00:09:50,381 --> 00:09:53,301
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>I don't make the rules. Haunters gonna haunt.</i></font>

175
00:09:59,432 --> 00:10:01,893
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Baby, are you killing yourself?</i></font>

176
00:10:01,976 --> 00:10:05,063
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm more embracing the win-win
of risking my life.</font>

177
00:10:06,356 --> 00:10:07,857
<font face="Serif" size="18">[dramatic music playing]</font>

178
00:10:14,030 --> 00:10:17,700
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Where's Mom and Summer?
- Oh, they're gone. Sorry, Morty.</font>

179
00:10:17,784 --> 00:10:18,743
<font face="Serif" size="18">"Gone" gone?</font>

180
00:10:18,827 --> 00:10:21,121
<font face="Serif" size="18">We spent a long time in that ice.</font>

181
00:10:21,204 --> 00:10:26,042
<font face="Serif" size="18">A gentle mutant licked us out,
but Beth got sick and Summer didn't thaw right.</font>

182
00:10:26,126 --> 00:10:27,460
<font face="Serif" size="18">[groaning]</font>

183
00:10:27,544 --> 00:10:30,547
<font face="Serif" size="18">With no one left to blame,
I finally had to deal with myself.</font>

184
00:10:30,630 --> 00:10:32,423
<font face="Serif" size="18">Buried my grief at Barnes and Noble.</font>

185
00:10:32,507 --> 00:10:36,469
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Four Agreements, Eat Pray Love,
</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">Frank Miller's <i>The Dark Knight Returns.</i></font>

186
00:10:36,553 --> 00:10:38,429
<font face="Serif" size="18">Learned to accept things for what they are.</font>

187
00:10:39,889 --> 00:10:42,642
<font face="Serif" size="18">In a few of these, the whole brain is still intact.</font>

188
00:10:42,725 --> 00:10:46,437
<font face="Serif" size="18">Makes you wonder if some people
were still in there just trapped in the horror.</font>

189
00:10:46,521 --> 00:10:48,231
<font face="Serif" size="18">Anyway, it's awesome protein.</font>

190
00:10:48,314 --> 00:10:53,236
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm so sorry, Dad,
but my real, original Dad beat the apocalypse.</font>

191
00:10:53,319 --> 00:10:55,655
<font face="Serif" size="18">I guess we all underestimated you.</font>

192
00:10:55,738 --> 00:10:59,200
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey, what's that game
we used to try to play as a family?</font>

193
00:10:59,284 --> 00:11:01,202
<font face="Serif" size="18">- The one we never finished?
- Downbeat.</font>

194
00:11:01,286 --> 00:11:04,873
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yes. Let's play Downbeat.
I can find it. We can finish now.</font>

195
00:11:04,956 --> 00:11:07,500
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah. You should totally do that.</font>

196
00:11:11,254 --> 00:11:13,089
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey, yeah, cool. I got it.</font>

197
00:11:13,173 --> 00:11:17,385
<font face="Serif" size="18">We'll play Downbeat and we'll camp here
tonight, then rebuild the house.</font>

198
00:11:17,468 --> 00:11:21,556
<font face="Serif" size="18">You know, we got food,
fresh water, and we've got family.</font>

199
00:11:21,639 --> 00:11:22,557
<font face="Serif" size="18">The fuck?</font>

200
00:11:24,767 --> 00:11:28,479
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Hermit Jerry] <i>I wrote this note in advance
in case you're wondering how I left so fast.</i></font>

201
00:11:28,563 --> 00:11:32,442
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>My plan is to wait for you to turn your back,
then I'm going to grab all your shit and split.</i></font>

202
00:11:32,525 --> 00:11:35,612
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Depending on how long you're out of the room,
you'll probably be thinking,</i></font>

203
00:11:35,695 --> 00:11:37,822
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>I can't be that far away
and you'll want to foll--</i></font>

204
00:11:40,700 --> 00:11:42,452
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Wrote this fast because had to set trap.</i></font>

205
00:11:42,535 --> 00:11:45,121
<font face="Serif" size="18">- <i>Thought you'd have cooler shit. See other note.
</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">- Motherf u--</font>

206
00:11:47,290 --> 00:11:50,376
<font face="Serif" size="18">Whoa, whoa, slow down! Slow down! Not cool!</font>

207
00:11:51,711 --> 00:11:52,921
<font face="Serif" size="18">What the hell, Dad?</font>

208
00:11:53,004 --> 00:11:56,633
<font face="Serif" size="18">Don't take it personal. One of the four agreements.
I don't remember the other three,</font>

209
00:11:56,716 --> 00:11:59,385
<font face="Serif" size="18">but I know Commissioner Gordon
was cool with Batman moving on.</font>

210
00:11:59,469 --> 00:12:02,764
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Batman doesn't abandon people.
- You abandoned us.</font>

211
00:12:02,847 --> 00:12:06,100
<font face="Serif" size="18">I deserve that. But, you know, it improved you.</font>

212
00:12:06,184 --> 00:12:08,436
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, am I cool enough for you now?</font>

213
00:12:08,519 --> 00:12:11,898
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, that was easy.
It only cost me fucking everything.</font>

214
00:12:11,981 --> 00:12:12,857
<font face="Serif" size="18">Whoa, hey, I--</font>

215
00:12:12,941 --> 00:12:15,652
<font face="Serif" size="18">You came back and talked about us
like we weren't people, Morty.</font>

216
00:12:15,735 --> 00:12:17,612
<font face="Serif" size="18">Then you bailed and left us to freeze.</font>

217
00:12:17,695 --> 00:12:19,322
<font face="Serif" size="18">I was apologizing for that earlier.</font>

218
00:12:19,405 --> 00:12:21,616
<font face="Serif" size="18">Your mom and sister died, Morty!</font>

219
00:12:23,076 --> 00:12:24,118
<font face="Serif" size="18">And I moved on.</font>

220
00:12:24,786 --> 00:12:26,079
<font face="Serif" size="18">From caring.</font>

221
00:12:26,162 --> 00:12:29,749
<font face="Serif" size="18">And that is the best deal
you will ever get. So take it.</font>

222
00:12:29,832 --> 00:12:30,875
<font face="Serif" size="18">Please don't go.</font>

223
00:12:30,959 --> 00:12:33,962
<font face="Serif" size="18">If Rick comes back,
we can find you a new reality,</font>

224
00:12:34,045 --> 00:12:36,631
<font face="Serif" size="18">a new Mom, a new Summer, a job.</font>

225
00:12:36,714 --> 00:12:38,258
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, you don't get it, kid.</font>

226
00:12:38,341 --> 00:12:40,885
<font face="Serif" size="18">Except for this conversation,
my life is perfect.</font>

227
00:12:40,969 --> 00:12:44,222
<font face="Serif" size="18">Rick was always right.
Everyone needs to let go.</font>

228
00:12:45,974 --> 00:12:47,225
<font face="Serif" size="18">[sobbing]</font>

229
00:12:48,268 --> 00:12:49,352
<font face="Serif" size="18">[leaves rustling]</font>

230
00:12:49,435 --> 00:12:52,730
<font face="Serif" size="18">Aw. You came back.
I guess we really did form a bond.</font>

231
00:12:52,814 --> 00:12:55,900
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ow! Hey, stop it! Get away from me!
No! Help!</font>

232
00:12:56,567 --> 00:12:58,945
<font face="Serif" size="18">All right. Pin dropped, Grandpa.</font>

233
00:12:59,028 --> 00:13:00,363
<font face="Serif" size="18">Come and get us.</font>

234
00:13:02,115 --> 00:13:04,284
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Rick] Come on, come on, come on!</font>

235
00:13:04,367 --> 00:13:06,577
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Diane] <i>Baby? Something to keep in mind.</i></font>

236
00:13:06,661 --> 00:13:11,666
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>If you were pulled home by whatever happened,
it's likely our target was as well.</i></font>

237
00:13:11,749 --> 00:13:15,461
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>It's also likely he's having
as much trouble leaving as you are.</i></font>

238
00:13:16,296 --> 00:13:18,089
<font face="Serif" size="18">He's trapped.</font>

239
00:13:19,674 --> 00:13:21,884
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [Summer] <i>Grandpa!
</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">- Oh, fuck, yes.</font>

240
00:13:26,097 --> 00:13:29,851
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [Summer] <i>Grandpa? Grandpa?
</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">- Summer! Gold star, always believed in you.</font>

241
00:13:29,934 --> 00:13:31,227
<font face="Serif" size="18">- <i>Now the hard part.
</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">- Hard part?</font>

242
00:13:31,311 --> 00:13:33,438
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Way worse things than me
can see that beacon too.</i></font>

243
00:13:33,521 --> 00:13:37,025
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Hunker down and protect it while I grab Morty.
Rick, out. Try to survive.</i></font>

244
00:13:37,108 --> 00:13:40,153
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, shit.
Domestic Mom should hide maybe.</font>

245
00:13:40,236 --> 00:13:43,239
<font face="Serif" size="18">- "Domestic Mom"?
- I mean, she's the cool space one.</font>

246
00:13:43,323 --> 00:13:45,992
<font face="Serif" size="18">Look, I'm not looking to get caught
in whatever this is.</font>

247
00:13:46,075 --> 00:13:48,745
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You guys can both hide maybe, hash it out.
- Quit talking down.</font>

248
00:13:48,828 --> 00:13:50,997
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm you with the patience to do laundry.</font>

249
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:52,957
<font face="Serif" size="18">Stop being jealous of our bond.</font>

250
00:13:53,041 --> 00:13:55,585
<font face="Serif" size="18">She ran from our choices.
I have to parent them.</font>

251
00:13:55,668 --> 00:13:59,088
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's not like I didn't care.
That's what the clone was for.</font>

252
00:13:59,172 --> 00:14:01,174
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [both screaming]
- Moms!</font>

253
00:14:01,257 --> 00:14:02,592
<font face="Serif" size="18">[sobbing]</font>

254
00:14:05,636 --> 00:14:07,055
<font face="Serif" size="18">[loud whooshing]</font>

255
00:14:14,479 --> 00:14:15,938
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Morty!
- Rick?</font>

256
00:14:16,022 --> 00:14:18,483
<font face="Serif" size="18">I knew it.
I knew you wouldn't leave me. Ow.</font>

257
00:14:18,566 --> 00:14:21,152
<font face="Serif" size="18">- The fuck?
- Did you see another Rick here?</font>

258
00:14:21,235 --> 00:14:23,654
<font face="Serif" size="18">Nondescript haircut, sci-fi jacket.</font>

259
00:14:23,738 --> 00:14:27,408
<font face="Serif" size="18">Of course you didn't see him.
You'd be dead or you'd be a bomb.</font>

260
00:14:27,492 --> 00:14:30,703
<font face="Serif" size="18">Do you feel bomb-y?
Nah, you would have blown up by now.</font>

261
00:14:30,787 --> 00:14:33,915
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wasn't the Rick here dead?
That's why you picked places, right?</font>

262
00:14:33,998 --> 00:14:38,669
<font face="Serif" size="18">Uh, well, your Rick, yeah, not dead.
More like not around.</font>

263
00:14:38,753 --> 00:14:41,339
<font face="Serif" size="18">When I met you, I was sort of hoping
he might turn up one day.</font>

264
00:14:41,422 --> 00:14:43,216
<font face="Serif" size="18">You son of a bitch. I got you.</font>

265
00:14:43,299 --> 00:14:46,969
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Where are we going?
- To kill your grandpa, little buddy.</font>

266
00:14:47,053 --> 00:14:48,012
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wait, what?</font>

267
00:14:48,096 --> 00:14:49,680
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't understand.</font>

268
00:14:49,764 --> 00:14:53,267
<font face="Serif" size="18">My original Rick killed your family
and you were just waiting for him to come back?</font>

269
00:14:53,351 --> 00:14:56,354
<font face="Serif" size="18">You understand fine. That was A-plus re-piping.</font>

270
00:14:56,437 --> 00:14:57,355
<font face="Serif" size="18">We're here.</font>

271
00:14:59,732 --> 00:15:03,152
<font face="Serif" size="18">This guy, Morty, he hates being found
but loves building elaborate shit.</font>

272
00:15:03,236 --> 00:15:05,947
<font face="Serif" size="18">Like playing a ton of <i>Minecraft,
</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">but all on a private server.</font>

273
00:15:06,030 --> 00:15:09,117
<font face="Serif" size="18">Am I in a fucking K-hole right now?
What is going on?</font>

274
00:15:12,286 --> 00:15:14,163
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Whoa, you found me.</i></font>

275
00:15:15,706 --> 00:15:20,420
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>I shoot the first monitor too.
Listen, I'm not here. Or am I?</i></font>

276
00:15:21,003 --> 00:15:23,798
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>There's the clone you found.
Or maybe it's me all naked.</i></font>

277
00:15:23,881 --> 00:15:27,260
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Just a little Keyser Söze.
Why would I admit it's not?</i></font>

278
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:31,264
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Yeah. Look at him. Look at him go.
Look at him dance. Or me.</i></font>

279
00:15:31,347 --> 00:15:33,766
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Again, it might be me, like a</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> Saw <i>thing.</i></font>

280
00:15:33,850 --> 00:15:35,059
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>I'm very sneaky.</i></font>

281
00:15:35,143 --> 00:15:38,146
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Here's a bunch of killbots to deal with
while you wrestle with that.</i></font>

282
00:15:42,775 --> 00:15:45,945
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>I don't know who I'm talking to.
It's all prerecorded.</i></font>

283
00:15:47,947 --> 00:15:50,992
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>But if you got this far,
you probably think you're real special.</i></font>

284
00:15:51,075 --> 00:15:52,076
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Tell you what.</i></font>

285
00:15:52,577 --> 00:15:54,871
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>There he goes. Maybe that was me.</i></font>

286
00:15:54,954 --> 00:15:57,331
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>If you follow him, we could do a big fight.</i></font>

287
00:15:57,415 --> 00:15:59,375
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>50% chance I'm not lying.</i></font>

288
00:16:01,294 --> 00:16:04,255
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Space Beth] <i>We're in trouble, asshole.
I shouldn't have to beg.</i></font>

289
00:16:04,338 --> 00:16:06,799
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Wait, my moms are in trouble?
- Those versions of them are.</font>

290
00:16:06,883 --> 00:16:09,802
<font face="Serif" size="18">We gotta save them.
Rick, this is an obvious trap.</font>

291
00:16:09,886 --> 00:16:11,971
<font face="Serif" size="18">- If you go down there, he's gonna kill you.
- Good.</font>

292
00:16:12,054 --> 00:16:13,055
<font face="Serif" size="18">What?</font>

293
00:16:15,016 --> 00:16:15,975
<font face="Serif" size="18">Now what?</font>

294
00:16:16,058 --> 00:16:18,561
<font face="Serif" size="18">If you don't care if you die,
why do you care if I die?</font>

295
00:16:18,644 --> 00:16:21,397
<font face="Serif" size="18">Knock it off. Get out of here.
You did this last season.</font>

296
00:16:21,481 --> 00:16:22,815
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're like a suicide bomber.</font>

297
00:16:22,899 --> 00:16:26,152
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Takes one to know one.
- You get it from him, not me.</font>

298
00:16:26,235 --> 00:16:27,487
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't know him.</font>

299
00:16:27,570 --> 00:16:29,697
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're my grandpa, Rick.</font>

300
00:16:29,780 --> 00:16:31,782
<font face="Serif" size="18">Rick and Morty. A hundred years.</font>

301
00:16:31,866 --> 00:16:35,453
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>This place totally might go up.
Here's a bunch of count downs.</i></font>

302
00:16:35,536 --> 00:16:37,455
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>One of them's probably accurate.</i></font>

303
00:16:39,373 --> 00:16:41,834
<font face="Serif" size="18">Fucking stupid fifth-dimensional stomach juices.</font>

304
00:16:41,918 --> 00:16:45,129
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sorry for the sitcom fight
and maybe getting us digested.</font>

305
00:16:45,213 --> 00:16:46,547
<font face="Serif" size="18">You've got incredible timing.</font>

306
00:16:46,631 --> 00:16:49,509
<font face="Serif" size="18">Don't be a bitch. I'm parenting.
Makes sense you don't recognize it.</font>

307
00:16:49,592 --> 00:16:51,010
<font face="Serif" size="18">You've been out of practice.</font>

308
00:16:51,093 --> 00:16:54,347
<font face="Serif" size="18">Good. Glad they have you.
I don't want to be Space Mom.</font>

309
00:16:54,430 --> 00:16:55,640
<font face="Serif" size="18">You've made that clear.</font>

310
00:16:55,723 --> 00:16:58,518
<font face="Serif" size="18">Just don't let Summer mistake
your rejection of her for good taste.</font>

311
00:16:58,601 --> 00:17:00,895
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm not trying to. It's all her.</font>

312
00:17:04,857 --> 00:17:08,903
<font face="Serif" size="18">It'd be cool if you were around more.
I don't wanna get married.</font>

313
00:17:08,986 --> 00:17:13,074
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm 17. My affection is the wind.
Don't try to compete for it.</font>

314
00:17:14,158 --> 00:17:16,327
<font face="Serif" size="18">I could hear every word of that
through the helmets.</font>

315
00:17:16,410 --> 00:17:18,287
<font face="Serif" size="18">Thank fuck I only had to kill most of them.</font>

316
00:17:18,371 --> 00:17:20,456
<font face="Serif" size="18">Jesus, that ship really has sailed.</font>

317
00:17:25,378 --> 00:17:29,257
<font face="Serif" size="18">And now we feast!</font>

318
00:17:31,592 --> 00:17:33,052
<font face="Serif" size="18">[screaming]</font>

319
00:17:33,135 --> 00:17:34,679
<font face="Serif" size="18">This emergency was oversold to me.</font>

320
00:17:34,762 --> 00:17:35,763
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Grandpa!
- Morty!</font>

321
00:17:35,846 --> 00:17:36,681
<font face="Serif" size="18">Moms!</font>

322
00:17:36,764 --> 00:17:40,268
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Wait, if they had to wear helmets--
- I do childproofing stuff while you're asleep.</font>

323
00:17:40,351 --> 00:17:42,687
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Why don't you childproof Dad?
- Great reminder.</font>

324
00:17:42,770 --> 00:17:44,313
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Wait. Ugh.
- Time to get Jerry.</font>

325
00:17:44,689 --> 00:17:50,528
<font face="Serif" size="18">Maybe I wouldn't be so uptight if I wasn't married
to an unemployed receptacle of human fear.</font>

326
00:17:50,611 --> 00:17:52,697
<font face="Serif" size="18">Get a job, Dad. It's been a decade.</font>

327
00:17:52,780 --> 00:17:56,492
<font face="Serif" size="18">Brutal. I know a good alligator park
if you wanna kill yourself.</font>

328
00:17:56,576 --> 00:17:58,244
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I got expelled today.
- [doorbell rings]</font>

329
00:17:58,327 --> 00:18:00,913
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You are so fucking dumb!
- What a horrible thing.</font>

330
00:18:00,997 --> 00:18:02,498
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Too bad, Morty.
- Hi, hon.</font>

331
00:18:02,582 --> 00:18:03,874
<font face="Serif" size="18">[gasps]</font>

332
00:18:03,958 --> 00:18:06,711
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oof. Some real Season 2 vibes in there.
You know what I'm saying?</font>

333
00:18:06,794 --> 00:18:11,882
<font face="Serif" size="18">Never thought I'd say this,
but I think I'm glad we spent that time divorced.</font>

334
00:18:11,966 --> 00:18:14,677
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Uh, one second.
- I'll build a swing set.</font>

335
00:18:14,760 --> 00:18:19,640
<font face="Serif" size="18">I may technically be from here,
but I'm a goddamn interdimensional traveler now</font>

336
00:18:19,724 --> 00:18:23,311
<font face="Serif" size="18">and all of you can kiss my sci-fi ass. [grunts]</font>

337
00:18:27,982 --> 00:18:28,858
<font face="Serif" size="18">[all laughing]</font>

338
00:18:28,941 --> 00:18:30,985
<font face="Serif" size="18">It gets me every time.</font>

339
00:18:31,068 --> 00:18:33,487
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wow, what an amazing joke I just told.</font>

340
00:18:33,571 --> 00:18:35,615
<font face="Serif" size="18">And also, what an adventure.</font>

341
00:18:35,698 --> 00:18:38,659
<font face="Serif" size="18">It doesn't matter where we're from
if we're together.</font>

342
00:18:38,743 --> 00:18:42,705
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Good final moral thing.
- This is everyone's original dimension now.</font>

343
00:18:42,788 --> 00:18:43,956
<font face="Serif" size="18">Great wrap-ups, kids.</font>

344
00:18:44,040 --> 00:18:46,751
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Ugh. You're back.
- Oh, shit. Season 2 Jerry.</font>

345
00:18:46,834 --> 00:18:49,295
<font face="Serif" size="18">Before you bust my balls,
can someone help with the shower?</font>

346
00:18:49,378 --> 00:18:51,380
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's colder than Beth on our anniversary.</font>

347
00:18:51,464 --> 00:18:53,924
<font face="Serif" size="18">Also, look who I found in Rick's room.</font>

348
00:18:54,008 --> 00:18:55,718
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mm, I'm Mr. Frundles.</font>

349
00:18:55,801 --> 00:18:58,512
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't care how cute he is,
we agreed no Boogens in the house.</font>

350
00:18:58,596 --> 00:19:00,514
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Season 2 Jerry, don't!
- Ow!</font>

351
00:19:00,598 --> 00:19:03,184
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [Beth] Mr. Frundles!
- Everybody in the car.</font>

352
00:19:04,101 --> 00:19:05,603
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm Mr. Frundles!</font>

353
00:19:05,686 --> 00:19:09,148
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I thought he was Mr. Frundles.
- Everybody in the car! Now!</font>

354
00:19:10,775 --> 00:19:15,321
<font face="Serif" size="18">[all] I'm Mr. Frundles!</font>

355
00:19:17,198 --> 00:19:19,742
<font face="Serif" size="18">What the fuck, Dad?
Why bring that thing into our house?</font>

356
00:19:19,825 --> 00:19:22,870
<font face="Serif" size="18">It was cute. Fuck.
We gotta find a new timeline now.</font>

357
00:19:22,953 --> 00:19:24,872
<font face="Serif" size="18">You know how hard that is without portals?</font>

358
00:19:24,955 --> 00:19:27,458
<font face="Serif" size="18">We gotta do the thing
with the rift and the beacon again.</font>

359
00:19:27,541 --> 00:19:29,585
<font face="Serif" size="18">The whole fucking episode
all over again.</font>

360
00:19:29,669 --> 00:19:31,671
<font face="Serif" size="18">Car, fabricate some vomit bags.</font>

361
00:19:31,754 --> 00:19:33,714
<font face="Serif" size="18">Can't we just go back and fix it?</font>

362
00:19:33,798 --> 00:19:38,844
<font face="Serif" size="18">[groans] I'm Mr. Frundles!</font>

363
00:19:41,180 --> 00:19:43,933
<font face="Serif" size="18">I can't believe portal travel's broken.</font>

364
00:19:44,016 --> 00:19:46,352
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I'll get to it when I get to it.
- Lift with your knees.</font>

365
00:19:46,435 --> 00:19:48,437
<font face="Serif" size="18">How many times have you done this?</font>

366
00:19:48,521 --> 00:19:49,480
<font face="Serif" size="18">[retches]</font>

367
00:19:50,523 --> 00:19:51,649
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, God.</font>

368
00:19:51,732 --> 00:19:55,236
<font face="Serif" size="18">- And you swear they die of natural causes?
- Mm-hm. Yep.</font>

369
00:19:55,319 --> 00:19:57,947
<font face="Serif" size="18">The same as our old timeline? Even my stuff?</font>

370
00:19:58,030 --> 00:20:01,409
<font face="Serif" size="18">Bit of a rush job.
So they do say "Parmesan" weird.</font>

371
00:20:01,492 --> 00:20:03,327
<font face="Serif" size="18">- How do they say--?
- Parmeesian.</font>

372
00:20:03,411 --> 00:20:05,287
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Jesus Christ.
- I could have left you guys.</font>

373
00:20:05,371 --> 00:20:08,833
<font face="Serif" size="18">You think the concept of family matters to me?
I'm not even your Rick.</font>

374
00:20:08,916 --> 00:20:11,252
<font face="Serif" size="18">- "I'm Denial Rick."
- [Beth] See you inside, Dad.</font>

375
00:20:11,752 --> 00:20:15,214
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sorry I was such a dance mom about Summer.
She's your daughter too.</font>

376
00:20:15,297 --> 00:20:16,757
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, boundaries are good.</font>

377
00:20:16,841 --> 00:20:20,219
<font face="Serif" size="18">But speaking of, maybe I've put up too many.</font>

378
00:20:20,302 --> 00:20:23,472
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Is it okay if I come around sometimes?
- That could be nice.</font>

379
00:20:23,556 --> 00:20:26,559
<font face="Serif" size="18">- That's a cute outfit.
- The one we always wear?</font>

380
00:20:30,771 --> 00:20:32,106
<font face="Serif" size="18">[groans]</font>

381
00:20:32,189 --> 00:20:33,274
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yes, Morty?</font>

382
00:20:33,357 --> 00:20:36,652
<font face="Serif" size="18">You promise I'm not bait
to make that Rick come back.</font>

383
00:20:36,736 --> 00:20:40,197
<font face="Serif" size="18">What? For you to be bait,
the guy would have to value something.</font>

384
00:20:40,281 --> 00:20:42,700
<font face="Serif" size="18">He truly does not give a shit.</font>

385
00:20:44,201 --> 00:20:46,036
<font face="Serif" size="18">He's the real deal.</font>

386
00:20:47,747 --> 00:20:48,998
<font face="Serif" size="18">Parmeesan.</font>

387
00:20:49,081 --> 00:20:50,249
<font face="Serif" size="18">Parmeesian.</font>

388
00:20:50,332 --> 00:20:52,042
<font face="Serif" size="18">Parmees-ian.</font>

389
00:20:52,126 --> 00:20:53,919
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Parmeesian.
- Parmeesian.</font>

390
00:20:54,003 --> 00:20:55,713
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Gross. I hate it.
- Yeah.</font>

391
00:20:56,088 --> 00:20:58,090
<font face="Serif" size="18">[theme music playing]</font>

392
00:21:30,414 --> 00:21:32,291
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hello? Morty?</font>

393
00:21:32,708 --> 00:21:35,044
<font face="Serif" size="18">- That one big rat?
- Whoa, this is a development.</font>

394
00:21:35,127 --> 00:21:37,129
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [shouts]
- Whoa, whoa, little guy.</font>

395
00:21:37,213 --> 00:21:38,839
<font face="Serif" size="18">Easy. You're a Jerry, right?</font>

396
00:21:38,923 --> 00:21:42,259
<font face="Serif" size="18">Never got too close to the concept.
Boy, you have really arc'd out.</font>

397
00:21:42,343 --> 00:21:43,636
<font face="Serif" size="18">Were you putting on pants?</font>

398
00:21:43,719 --> 00:21:46,305
<font face="Serif" size="18">What? No, I was naked to fuck with a guy.</font>

399
00:21:46,388 --> 00:21:49,642
<font face="Serif" size="18">Speaking of,
did you talk to me or a little kid around here?</font>

400
00:21:50,226 --> 00:21:51,560
<font face="Serif" size="18">Maybe. Why?</font>

401
00:21:52,061 --> 00:21:55,481
<font face="Serif" size="18">If you hate them too,
I could be down for a little team-up.</font>

402
00:21:55,564 --> 00:21:59,109
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't "team up" anymore.
Managing people, such a headache.</font>

403
00:22:00,110 --> 00:22:03,280
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Fatality. Jerry wins.
- [gasping]</font>

404
00:22:07,868 --> 00:22:10,830
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, goddamn, dude. Badass.</font>

405
00:22:11,914 --> 00:22:12,957
<font face="Serif" size="18">[groaning]</font>

406
00:22:13,874 --> 00:22:15,251
<font face="Serif" size="18">Why are you here?</font>

407
00:22:15,334 --> 00:22:20,047
<font face="Serif" size="18">Buddy, I have been asking myself
that exact same question.</font>

